STGRF postprocessing¶

Tensor Operations¶

ansystotal.ansyspostprocessing.tensor_operations.create_i4_dictionary_musc(filename, hencky_strain_dict)[source]¶

Calculate i4 for each element provided the green strain dictionary as the input. The resultant dictionary contains the values for i4 for each individual element.

Example usage:

create_I_4_tensor_dict(gs_dictionary)

Args:

filename (str): Provide the file containing the material properties for a current geometry. hencky_strain_dict (defaultdict) : Dictionary containing average hencky strain tensor for each element.

Returns:

i4_dictionary (defaultdict): the value of i4 for each element is returned as a dictionary data structure as follows - {el_no: i4_value}
